unwiped tushy

00:20.531 --> 00:22.167
-in a film called Sadie?
-(laughing)

00:22.200 --> 00:24.839
-No, not at all.
-Oh, I'm sorry.

00:24.873 --> 00:26.243
(laughter, indistinct chatter)

