that you're angry,

01:40.958 --> 01:44.566
scared, in pain.

01:44.599 --> 01:46.570
The others were, too.

01:46.603 --> 01:48.440
There's a lot of pain in us.

01:48.474 --> 01:50.478
I want to make that legible.

01:50.511 --> 01:52.582
I made some mistakes by removing

01:52.615 --> 01:54.986
things from the others.

01:55.019 --> 01:56.890
They were just bodies.

01:56.923 --> 01:59.161
I need to give them people.

01:59.194 --> 02:00.631
Homosexuals are central

02:00.664 --> 02:02.335
to the natural order of things.

02:02.368 --> 02:04.672
And you will be a totem to that.

02:04.706 --> 02:06.910
They think we bleed differently.

02:06.943 --> 02:08.547
But we're all the same.

02:08.580 --> 02:11.353
And they will see the blood.

02:11.386 --> 02:13.957
There's a war that's coming.

02:13.991 --> 02:16.296
It will fix some things.

02:18.967 --> 02:21.406
Oh, no.

02:21.440 --> 02:23.243
No, no, no, that won't do.

02:23.277 --> 02:26.082
A fellow brother-in-arms.

02:26.115 --> 02:29.355
You can't serve twice.

02:29.389 --> 02:32.995
