there's no use in going?

08:33.439 --> 08:35.176
The NY-fucking-PD!

08:35.209 --> 08:36.979
-Taxi!
-(honking)
-GINO: They hate us. The police

08:37.013 --> 08:39.083
-hate us. This city hates us.
-Fuck you!

08:39.117 --> 08:41.054
GINO:
And I know people in City Hall

08:41.087 --> 08:43.625
and in the NYPD-- gay men--

08:43.659 --> 08:45.964
and some of them
I know really well.

08:45.997 --> 08:47.567
