17:47.212 --> 17:49.216
Thanks for picking me up.

17:49.250 --> 17:52.189
I wanted a witness so they know
someone knows I was there.

17:52.222 --> 17:54.060
Thought I was gonna
have to bail you out.

17:54.093 --> 17:56.064
