for hurting their feelings.

18:00.839 --> 18:02.142
This city's gone insane.

18:02.176 --> 18:03.878
The cops are just as bad
as the criminals.

18:03.913 --> 18:05.716
It was always like that.

18:05.749 --> 18:07.753
You were just too white
to notice.

18:07.786 --> 18:09.724
Enough with this doom and gloom.

18:09.757 --> 18:11.627
Summer is here. Lighten up.

18:11.661 --> 18:13.732
You should come out
with me tonight.

18:13.765 --> 18:16.604
There's a party.
It will blow your mind.

18:16.637 --> 18:18.141
It's in the most run-down part
of the city.

18:18.174 --> 18:19.810
