and poetry readings.

18:33.204 --> 18:35.008
Real Parisian shit.

18:35.042 --> 18:38.114
He likes the contrast of
the decadence with the squalor.

18:38.148 --> 18:39.985
He sounds like an asshole.

18:40.018 --> 18:41.721
He is, but so what?

18:41.754 --> 18:43.725
All the cool downtown artists
will be there.

18:43.758 --> 18:46.030
