He said,

20:45.735 --> 20:47.372
"You can try
to tell the police about me,

20:47.406 --> 20:49.877
but they won't do anything.

20:49.911 --> 20:51.982
They don't want to."

20:52.015 --> 20:54.687
A fucking psychopathic killer

20:54.720 --> 20:56.123
knows more about the cops
than you do.

20:56.157 --> 20:57.826
-Not fair, Gino.
-Oh, really?

20:57.860 --> 20:59.931
-No.
-Okay, so talk.
What are you doing?

20:59.965 --> 21:02.135
