you know the facts.

21:02.169 --> 21:04.006
Tell me, how's
the investigation going?

21:04.039 --> 21:05.709
-These things take time.
-I gave you

21:05.742 --> 21:07.246
a perfect description
of this guy,

21:07.279 --> 21:08.848
and we know he must have
been in the service.

21:08.882 --> 21:10.385
You can't fucking
do anything with that?

21:10.418 --> 21:11.888
What about The Brownstone?

21:11.922 --> 21:13.424
Anybody bother
to go over there? Maybe--

21:13.458 --> 21:15.128
I don't know,
I'm just spit balling here--

21:15.161 --> 21:17.799
question the fucking staff?

21:20.772 --> 21:22.376
When are you gonna
tell them you're gay?

21:22.409 --> 21:24.380
Oh, you think that'll help?

21:24.413 --> 21:25.849
-Huh?
-It's just...

21:25.882 --> 21:28.187
