for a man to live a lie,

21:28.221 --> 21:30.458
especially one this big.

21:30.492 --> 21:32.931
I just left my wife, Gino.

21:35.903 --> 21:37.739
Okay.

21:37.773 --> 21:39.877
All right, fine.

21:39.911 --> 21:43.017
But we're not gonna
just sit here on our asses

21:43.051 --> 21:44.720
