-Right.

22:01.955 --> 22:04.293
Right.
So pick one.

22:04.326 --> 22:06.230
Let's go.

22:08.434 --> 22:10.438
What's the matter?

22:10.472 --> 22:12.342
Those places not your scene?

22:12.376 --> 22:14.280
You know they're not.

22:16.050 --> 22:17.753
-Well...
-(groans)

22:20.792 --> 22:23.331
-(groans)
-Tonight, they are.

22:23.364 --> 22:25.769
