to a party.

23:58.321 --> 24:01.427
Just you and me.

24:01.460 --> 24:03.297
How do you know
what kind of fun I like?

24:03.331 --> 24:04.566
I know the bar you're at.

24:07.572 --> 24:09.143
Why don't you come meet me here?

24:09.176 --> 24:11.414
No. Come to me.

24:11.447 --> 24:14.988
I have everything we need
to have the time of our lives.

24:15.956 --> 24:17.960
Okay. Where?

24:17.994 --> 24:21.902
17 Great Jones. Apartment 11.

24:21.935 --> 24:23.438
It's the one in the basement.

24:23.471 --> 24:25.442
The door will be open.

24:25.475 --> 24:27.312
All right.

24:27.345 --> 24:29.583
I'm Stewart, by the way.

24:29.616 --> 24:31.053
Stu.

24:31.087 --> 24:33.191
