28:26.724 --> 28:29.496
-Sometimes.
-Don't you think
we can do better?

28:32.435 --> 28:35.174
Find another way
to connect that doesn't...

28:35.208 --> 28:37.178
just leave you with

28:37.212 --> 28:39.316
nothing but the clap
in your throat?

28:39.349 --> 28:40.451
Maybe.

28:43.891 --> 28:46.196
What do you have in mind?

28:46.230 --> 28:48.567
(chuckles)
Tonight?

28:52.642 --> 28:55.682
We could just...

28:55.715 --> 28:59.189
get a drink and food and...

28:59.222 --> 29:02.195
talk.

29:02.228 --> 29:04.266
-♪ ♪
-(indistinct chatter)

29:15.888 --> 29:18.494
All right.
Let's go to work.

29:21.767 --> 29:23.804
Pick your pleasure.

29:25.375 --> 29:27.612
-Somewhere over the rainbow.
-What if I just wanted

29:27.645 --> 29:29.349
