and grab some toilet paper.

29:32.222 --> 29:33.357
Hmm?

29:33.391 --> 29:35.628
We should split up.

29:41.240 --> 29:43.611
-Alana, hey.
-Gino.

29:45.281 --> 29:48.521
Well, now I know why
I've been so depressed.

29:48.554 --> 29:51.226
Haven't seen you in weeks. It's
horrible what happened to you.

29:51.260 --> 29:53.497
I'll be okay. This is Patrick.

29:53.531 --> 29:56.503
-Hello.
-Nice to meet you.

29:59.276 --> 30:01.647
So, what are you working on now?

30:01.680 --> 30:03.250
Who's hiding
in that dark closet you like

30:03.284 --> 30:04.553
-to throw light into?
-GINO: I'm actually

30:04.586 --> 30:06.824
writing about
the murders right now.

30:06.857 --> 30:08.794
Can't get them out of my head.
They're terrible.

30:08.828 --> 30:10.531
Makes me sick to my stomach.

30:10.565 --> 30:12.702
Oh, but if you're here
about that,

30:12.736 --> 30:15.308
-I suggest you turn around
and go somewhere else.
-Why?

30:15.341 --> 30:18.447
'Cause I can't have this place
associated with any of that.

30:18.481 --> 30:19.917
My bosses don't pay taxes

30:19.951 --> 30:21.386
and they settle their problems
in Jersey,

30:21.420 --> 30:22.689
if you know what I mean.

30:22.722 --> 30:24.292
Well, I'm just here
to look around,

30:24.326 --> 30:25.561
-take the temperature.
-Well, the temperature

30:25.595 --> 30:27.399
is rising, fast.

30:27.432 --> 30:28.634
I'll leave The Ditch out of it,
I promise.

30:28.667 --> 30:30.906
-I don't know.
-I promise.

30:30.939 --> 30:32.409
(sighs)

30:32.442 --> 30:34.413
Okay.

30:34.446 --> 30:35.916
But I'm gonna hold you
to that promise.

30:35.949 --> 30:37.987
You won't like Jersey,

30:38.020 --> 30:40.291
especially not from the inside
of an oil drum.

30:40.324 --> 30:42.395
Nice to meet you.

30:42.429 --> 30:44.433
Likewise.

30:47.472 --> 30:49.443
Can I get two?

30:49.476 --> 30:52.849
♪ Walk the night,
hey, gonna walk the night ♪

30:52.882 --> 30:54.753
