31:56.410 --> 31:58.814
I don't see him anymore.

31:58.848 --> 32:00.818
What is this?

32:00.852 --> 32:02.923
Strange-ass drink
for this place.

32:04.059 --> 32:06.063
-Barb came to see me.
-Hmm?

32:06.096 --> 32:09.870
